{"tid":311011,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"AIA intern 求解","createTime":"2017-07-06T09:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:05:08.000Z","uid":115875,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d003b556d2459db678cdb4bee4c13efa933d1b6","tid":311011,"uid":115875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過做AIA啲internship programme?<br />\n<br />\n最近俾個aia嘅人揾去做個叫&ldquo;Challenge university tournament&rdquo; 嘅internship programme <br />\n佢話會教有關 wealth management 同 business 方面嘅技巧<br />\n但小弟其實唔係讀緊 business 嘅課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇其他人又話 aia 有啲 summer intern 係想氹人幫佢 sell 保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係又有啲人話可以整靚個cv<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位有冇試過做 aia 啲 intern?<br />\n可唔可以話俾小弟知其實伏唔伏？<br />\n<br />\n利申：year 1"},{"pid":"5c897c3f7b5dc09181e4e230cae0b143d9df393a","tid":311011,"uid":12625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"咪撚去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333b82000e54bbbc6be57256164231c144b751ab","tid":311011,"uid":104838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"去左，就做死一世保險嫁啦"},{"pid":"3e6590dcd72465a547356f6fb4ce382512655916","tid":311011,"uid":25659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"整靚cv?<br />\n見到aia都已經覺得整衰份cv 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b83e52f49179a44f16f5402041cc1439dde5d0","tid":311011,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"伏"},{"pid":"9e32b6abfcc7581942553e662134dbabf36d3134","tid":311011,"uid":63187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score